#include <bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
int main() {
	vector<int> v(1000001),div(1000001);
	int t,i,j,n;
	v[1]=1;
	v[0]=1;
	for(i=2;i<=1000000;i++)
	{
		if(v[i]==0)
		{
			div[i]=1;
			for(j=2*i;j<=1000000;j=j+i)
			{
				div[j]++;
				v[j]=1;
			}
		}
	}
	scanf("%d",&t);
	while(t--)
	{
	   	scanf("%d",&n);
	   	if(v[div[n]]==0)
	   		printf("Funny\n");
	   	else
	   		printf("Not Funny\n");
	}
	return 0;
}
